* Advanced\nSchedule (Cron)
** Cron Fields (left to right)
***_ Seconds (0-59)
***_ Minutes (0-59)
***_ Hours (0-23)
***_ Day of month (1-31)
***_ Month (1-12 / JAN-DEC)
***_ Day of week (1-7 / SUN-SAT)
***_ Year (optional)
** Special Characters
***_ * = all values
***_ ? = no specific value
***_ - = range (10-12)
***_ , = list (MON,WED,FRI)
***_ / = increment (0/15)
***_ L = last day
***_ # = nth occurrence (6#3)
** Examples
***_ 0 0 12 * * ? = daily noon
***_ 0 15 10 ? * MON-FRI = weekdays 10:15
***_ 0 30 6 ? * 6L = last Friday 6:30
@endmindmap
